Feminized Seeds

Success in the hands of experts and beginners

Choosing feminized cannabis seeds simplifies considerably the growing process. Experienced growers know exactly how important that is, but maybe those who are taking their first steps in this world are not aware of the many advantages these type of strains can bring about. Endless and really varied benefits that are worth taking into account when deciding which type of seeds to buy and grow. When it comes to feminized seeds, the following aspects could help you make up your mind:

  • 99% of the plants are sure to be female, which means time, space and money are greatly saved.
  • The arduous process of selecting and removing male plants is avoided, and so is the risk of accidental pollination of female plants.

If you are new to this concepts and to better understand the benefits of growing weed using feminized cannabis seeds you can check this article on Cannabis Cultivation out  (be sure to scroll down to the Feminized Seeds anchor).

Feminized marijuana genetics imbued with old-school traits

As all Humboldt Seed Organization cannabis seeds, the feminized collection lovingly preserves every trait inherited from the legendary strains developed in California during the 60's. Our feminized seeds are cultivated following the same criteria as in that time, with authentic genetics in a 100% organic manner. The ideas on which our philosophy is based are crystal clear and have allowed us to set the following premises:

  • Collective work with a participatory approach and many common interests.
  • Respect for the environment and preservation of the surrounding area.
  • Conservation of natural resources.
  • Support of the sustainability concept to set and reach our aims.

The aforementioned ideas lead to the development of high-quality strains that have nothing to envy to "old-school" genetics and that allow us to provide our customers with the best feminized cannabis seeds: potency, flavors and aromas of yesteryear, and amazing yields.

Feminized cannabis seeds to cater to all tastes

At Humboldt Seed Organization, we have created a catalogue full of contrasts featuring an incredibly varied range of delicious combinations to suit all kinds of tastes and occasions. Their effects, flavors and aromas are able to stir amazing strong sensations in whoever gives them a try.

Here you are some reference strains worth bearing in mind when purchasing in our feminized cannabis seeds' section:

  • Blue Dream. Everybody's favourite strain. Try them and you won't be disappointed at their potent and long-lasting effect and their heavy-yielding properties!
  • Pineapple Skunk. A stable, fast-flowering and potent Skunk with balanced aromas and infinite flavors.
  • Master Kush. A seed with strong origins and amazing yielding properties. Its deeply citric fragrance warmly wraps you as the long-lasting high takes places.
  • Lemon Thai Kush. A high-yielding Sativa with refreshing Haze-like flavors and aromas. Classic and reliable.
  • Blueberry Headband. Marvelous overall balance, mind-blowing potency, outstanding heavy-yielding properties, and fruity, spiced flavors that are a treat for the senses.
  • OG Kush. Exclusive flavors and scents accompanied by a pleasantly soothing effect. A strain of worship that brings you happiness.
  • 707 Truthband by Emerald Mountain. An innovative version of the world-renowned OG Kush that boasts the complexity of Californian marijuana. Strong personality within easy reach.
  • Bubba Kush. A pureblood Indica that tastes of soil and delivers a nice relaxing high.
  • Lemon Garlic OG. A "made in California" prodigy that awakens all senses.
  • Mango Sapphire. This Californian hybrid proudly showcases really interesting soothing properties. A gem that gives off notes of exotic fruits, coconut and mango.
  • Chemdawg. A powerful strain capable of producing incredibly bountiful crops in record time. It smells and tastes of lemon, pineapple and gasoline. Suitable for users accustomed to consuming extremely potent strains.

We are certain our feminized seeds will allow you to discover a completely new world of possibilities.

Try them and give us your opinion!
